 * should be capable of" proof.
 *
 * On failure the return code is the 1-based index of the first faculty whose
 * selftest did not return 99 — so a red result names the exact organ.
 *
 * THE HOST LAW (discovered + pinned by bisection 2026-06-09): the Windows x64 loader REFUSES
 * any image with SizeOfImage >= 0x77000000 (1904 MiB) — ERROR_BAD_EXE_FORMAT regardless of free
 * commit (1903 MiB-BSS loads, 1904 does not; pure-C repro).  This one-image form's union BSS is
 * ~1.93 GiB, so the image CANNOT load on this host — this file remains the conjunction's
 * one-image SPECIFICATION; the RUNNABLE proof is the weight-balanced trio indep_cap_a/b/c.iii
